data.description: DESIGNED TO IMPRESS, INTRODUCING THE BENEDICT. This luxurious ranch home is sure to dazzle your dinner guests from the moment they walk in. With its elegant foyer, complete with tray ceiling, and its awe-inspiring great room, this generous floorplan is ideal for cocktail parties or simply winding down with a glass of wine. What are you waiting for? Come on in and enjoy the life of leisure that The Benedict can offer you.All prices, promotions and specifications are subject to change at any time without notice based on the discretion of Veridian Homes. Amenities: Award-winning, high-performance home, Convenient kitchen island with sink, Energy expert certified, Flex room off foyer, for formal dining, office, etc., Full basement, Kitchen open to great room/dining area, Nine foot ceilings throughout first floor, with ten foot ceilings in great room, Quartz or granite kitchen counters, Separate mudroom and laundry room with sink, Smart Home+ technology, Tray ceiling in foyer, Walk-in closets in secondary bedrooms
